room_title: Escape room "The Bunker" by Puzzle Room Tahoe in South Lake Tahoe
room_description: You came to Lake Tahoe for a relaxing vacation but things took a turn when you were kidnapped and knocked unconscious. You awaken and discover you have been locked in a bunker. After taking a look around it appears this was a secret CIA location. But it has now been seized by a criminal organization. They have evil plans and it's evident you are the only hope. Identify the criminals and escape The Bunker before it's too late.
